  &lt;!-- &lt;property name=&quot;maxDelayMs&quot; value=&quot;30000&quot; /&gt; --&gt;

respectCrawlDelayUpToSeconds has to do with the &quot;crawl-delay&quot; directive in
robots.txt and is probably not your issue since you&#39;re seeing a minimum
delay of 3 seconds, which matches up with the default minDelayMs.

The easiest thing to do is set maxDelayMs to a small value. That will
override minDelayMs.

